      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELLEN ROSE (6) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 4.5 lengths win at this track in a handy 19.31. Jumping from the pinch draw but has the ability and in winning form. Can continue the winning form. SLEEK KARMA (1) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 350m (19.43). Expected to run well. ELECTRIC MAN (7) was in the minors two back (25.61) at Q Lakeside but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of seven starts. Great chance to atone. BELL MAC PRINCE (2) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
